= Zodiac

A Rails plugin to get the zodiac sign on a given date.

== Example

  zodiac_sign_for(Time.utc(2000, "jun", 12))
  # => "Gemini"

  zodiac_sign_for(1118)  # November 18
  # => "Scorpio"

  zodiac_sign_for(612)  # June 12
  # => "Gemini"


